      <title>特斯拉在中国对 120 万辆汽车进行维修，以解决安全问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/tesla-deploys-fix-to-1-2-million-cars-in-china-on-safety-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司将向其在华约 120 万辆汽车（约占其在华销售汽车的一半）发布软件更新，以解决车辆动力转向和后视摄像头存在安全隐患的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/tesla-deploys-fix-to-1-2-million-cars-in-china-on-safety-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 08:12:09 GMT</pubDate>
