      <title>Paschi 出人意料地以 130 亿欧元收购 Mediobanca 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/monte-paschi-makes-all-share-takeover-offer-for-mediobanca</link>
      <description><![CDATA[锡耶纳蒙特帕斯基银行 (Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena SpA) 提出以 133 亿欧元（139 亿美元）的全股票交易收购其规模更大的竞争对手 Mediobanca SpA，这是意大利银行业一系列收购尝试中最新的意外转折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/monte-paschi-makes-all-share-takeover-offer-for-mediobanca</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 06:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
